[FFFFFF]Old Living Quarters:[-] Storage niches; decaying rushes on floor; heaped remains of a bed. Dozens of oversized pill bugs, each the size of a fist, scurry about the room. These insects are unsightly, but harmless. Orcs enjoy them roasted as snacks, and a party offering pill bugs as bribes will enjoy a -2 reaction modifier with any orcs encountered. 
